{"tid":2081663,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府宣傳港區國安法花費約688萬元","createTime":"2020-06-27T11:42:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T16:25:53.000Z","uid":37554,"like":5,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4043aeb1e71b7d3a6fd21851dfee62318457fcf7","tid":2081663,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:42:44.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政府在電視報章及社交媒體等平台宣傳港區國安法，總開支約688萬元。<br />\n<br />\n全國人大通過訂立港區國安法後，政府推出一系列宣傳廣告，其中在電視、電台及社交媒體平台宣傳費用涉約26萬元，報章廣告費用約25萬，其他廣告，包括公共交通工具廣告、戶外廣告牌、橫額、海報等，費用為約40萬元。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=395937\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D395937&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFvUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=b21009fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D395937&h=4b8e7166\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=395937</a>"},{"pid":"83b5271ae5921c7fdf304c6bcf7fa1c8a0ea31f8","tid":2081663,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:43:42.000Z","msg":"浪費公帑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【語重心長】【德國戰線】城堡守衛戰 之 德國其實都有手足<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2081643\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2081643</a>"},{"pid":"be5b87db3411eae9c0bfb8614a298b4509f81e28","tid":2081663,"uid":193642,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:44:08.000Z","msg":"咁平？全部有特價？"},{"pid":"8c79c3b0f9719c96be09f63183fec15171c8b6fa","tid":2081663,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:45:21.000Z","msg":"主要喺tvb賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n私私相授<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dcc77430cca50494f48d2a199e32de39861876b","tid":2081663,"uid":122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime